                            Dodaj wpis
                        </button>
                        <button onclick="hideAddEntryForm()" class="bg-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-xl font-semibold transition-all duration-300 flex-1 min-w-32">
